snippet.title: STUFF'D Official Trailer | Short Horror Game by Banq Games
snippet.description:
Today is Grandma’s funeral. Your brother David stopped by her house after work to pick up Grandpa but no one has heard from them. That’s when you come in..

Welcome to STUFF’D.

Itch.io Page: https://banq-games.itch.io/stuffd-game
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BanqGames
